The paper discusses a method for extracting core claims from scientific articles using a controlled natural language. This involves techniques related to natural language processing, information retrieval, and machine learning, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
